This directory has the mdview software (3D molecular viewer).

There are some files you should read.

    INSTALL
      Details on compiling and installing mdview.
    mdview.1
      The mdview manual pages.
    ChangeLog
      Describes changes between Version 3.50.0 and current release
      of mdview.
    NEWS
    COPYING
    AUTHORS

There is a web site at http://www.chem.nagoya-u.ac.jp/bar/mdview/
-- see that site for the latest updates.
(However, Japanese only, now.)

Report any bugs to akinori@kobe-u.ac.jp

